{"tid":177804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「聽到BuliBuli好困擾」　日本超商貼公告勸大便小聲一點","createTime":"2017-03-29T06:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T07:49:59.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9458bf1d1fdc0c774d6dc8e7ba195efc08e97267","tid":177804,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>「聽到BuliBuli好困擾」　日超商貼公告勸大便小聲一點</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2423/d2423069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2423%2Fd2423069.jpg&h=f922d26c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在「解放」太大聲也不行？日本連鎖超商「Daily Yamazaki」大阪的一間分店中，有網友拍下廁所中的告示，竟然是希望客人大號的時候小聲一點，還用狀聲詞清楚描述「排放」過程的聲音，幽默的公告引發討論。<br />\n<br />\n「Daily Yamazaki」是日本的老字號便利商店，店內也多半有提供廁所，不過日本人非常重視如廁的禮貌和隱私，甚至有會放音樂馬桶，用來掩蓋上廁所的聲音。日前有網友在大阪的一間分店中發現這個公告。先是在最上面用紅色字寫出大大的「拜託了」，再加上兩個誠懇的土下座小人，請求的事項竟是希望店內上廁所的客人大便時可以小聲一點。<br />\n<br />\n公告內容寫說，最近收到投訴，有些客人在使用廁所時，「大便的發出的噪音，造成其他客人購物時的困擾」。另外還生動的描述便便的聲音，「如果聽到ブリブリ（BuliBuli）的聲音，會造成正在購物的客人留下不愉快的消費經驗。」<br />\n<br />\n最後又再度誠意十足的說，「在大便的時候呢，希望大家可以協助配合，把『BuliBuli』的聲音用小一點的好了呢。」爆笑的公告引起網友討論，有人說「這真的太難了啦，哪有辦法控制啊」、「不過在購物的時候聽到這種聲音真的有點囧」、「光從聲音就覺得好臭！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82cb5cc7558da5d4fd22258d1472475713f7096","tid":177804,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"係公司廁所成日聽到人柯屎柯到好似俾人屌屎眼咁呻吟"},{"pid":"94e35e57f073ff74f9bdbec7d638be2e9d8512df","tid":177804,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:14:07.000Z","msg":"睇怕要學某藥廠嘅乳酸菌膠囊廣告，標語大書：「增強『痾』力！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2850a9d7372f50e93a46054c2bc4a853958e71","tid":177804,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"又幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又好慘"},{"pid":"0c0ed51686a9b43020ead5d7e6f43d36298232b2","tid":177804,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"其實音樂馬桶都唔夠大聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用左都無咩用"},{"pid":"433b4a59bb54fc92dc5743fea369a78a61bf474e","tid":177804,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"日本有d廁所可以播沖廁聲蓋住爆石聲<br />\n果時係咁禁黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61be44df788825ff7f97d42b51cf8cacf481f0f","tid":177804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"bubugi"},{"pid":"7b968bc52514cbea0bbbe2a33db9a1d34ad06daf","tid":177804,"uid":42735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"BuliBuli係咪蠟筆小新咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489e40ef9909dc299bf96fb0aabb3d5de24befd2","tid":177804,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"pipapapapababa"},{"pid":"fdd52b4793dea645dea578dde2a0596f8c67344f","tid":177804,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑左出黎，加個post有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452251bf45c29462aec5f7570762cefdf38f9901","tid":177804,"uid":41076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BuliBuli係咪蠟筆小新咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不理不理左衞門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b06ea6a7cce9fc40b516a17b1a